<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 15 May 2024 10:08:24 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列独立日，以色列国防军士兵在加沙南部被杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-15/ty-article/.premium/idf-soldier-killed-in-southern-gaza-on-israels-independence-day/0000018f-7b63-dd07-adbf-fb73b1500000</link><description>中士。 Ira Yair Gispan，19 岁，来自佩塔提克瓦，是 Amit 和 Talia 的儿子，学习软件工程。他过去的老师形容他有“迷人的微笑”，这让老师很难对他生气</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 May 2024 09:58:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-15/ty-article/.premium/idf-soldier-killed-in-southern-gaza-on-israels-independence-day/0000018f-7b63-dd07-adbf-fb73b1500000</guid></item><item><title>以色列外交部透露，持有外交护照的人不到3%</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-15/ty-article/.premium/israels-foreign-ministry-reveals-less-than-3-of-diplomatic-passport-holders/0000018f-7b28-d430-a38f-ffecc5ec0000</link><description>商务部表示，未列出可能危害国家安全、持有人人身安全或对外关系的人员以及未成年人的姓名。亚伊尔·内塔尼亚胡 (Yair Netanyahu) 被列入名单，尽管他没有达到入选标准</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 May 2024 09:04:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-15/ty-article/.premium/israels-foreign-ministry-reveals-less-than-3-of-diplomatic-passport-holders/0000018f-7b28-d430-a38f-ffecc5ec0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列提议：只有在达成协议结束真主党敌对行动后才与黎巴嫩进行边界谈判</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-15/ty-article/.premium/israeli-proposal-border-talks-with-lebanon-only-after-deal-to-end-hezbollah-hostilities/0000018f-78be-d599-ab8f-7cff1cd90000</link><description>贝鲁特渴望尽快就新边界问题展开谈判，但以色列官员宁愿等到战斗结束。根据法律，任何以色列领土的转让都必须进行全民公投——内塔尼亚胡可能很难获得支持</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 May 2024 05:13:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-15/ty-article/.premium/israeli-proposal-border-talks-with-lebanon-only-after-deal-to-end-hezbollah-hostilities/0000018f-78be-d599-ab8f-7cff1cd90000</guid></item><item><title>莎拉·埃尔弗雷斯 (Sarah Elfreth) 赢得马里兰州初选，AIPAC 取得 2024 年最大选举胜利</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-05-15/ty-article/.premium/aipac-scores-its-biggest-electoral-victory-of-2024-as-sarah-elfreth-wins-maryland-primary/0000018f-7a3e-dd07-adbf-fb7e65c10000</link><description>埃尔弗雷斯在马里兰州初选中赢得众议院空缺席位，这被认为是亲以色列游说团体急需的路线修正，此前该团体之前在加州的重大投资未能阻止选民选择戴夫·明 (Dave Min)。</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 May 2024 03:22:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-05-15/ty-article/.premium/aipac-scores-its-biggest-electoral-victory-of-2024-as-sarah-elfreth-wins-maryland-primary/0000018f-7a3e-dd07-adbf-fb7e65c10000</guid></item><item><title>正统派政客和以色列国防官员之间的僵局使极端正统派征兵陷入困境</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-15/ty-article/.premium/impasse-between-haredi-pols-israeli-defense-chiefs-leaves-ultra-orthodox-draft-in-limbo/0000018f-78ea-d430-a38f-fdee86e40000</link><description>正统派政客坚称，本杰明·内塔尼亚胡政府采取的任何招募计划都将遭到反对，并暗示不同的联盟可以确保为选民提供更好的协议</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 May 2024 03:00:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-15/ty-article/.premium/impasse-between-haredi-pols-israeli-defense-chiefs-leaves-ultra-orthodox-draft-in-limbo/0000018f-78ea-d430-a38f-fdee86e40000</guid></item><item><title>美国向以色列提供10亿美元武器援助</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-15/ty-article-live/state-dept-moves-1b-weapons-aid-for-israel-to-congressional-review-u-s-officials-say/0000018f-7a05-d604-af8f-7f05810c0000</link><description>以色列国防军确认真主党战地指挥官在黎巴嫩南部的以色列无人机袭击中丧生 ■ 联合国表示，随着以色列国防军坦克深入拉法，超过 50 万人逃离加沙北部拉法 ■ 极右翼内塔尼亚胡部长领导游行，呼吁重新安置加沙地带 ■ 报道：开罗埃及官员称考虑降级与以色列的外交关系</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 May 2024 02:18:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-15/ty-article-live/state-dept-moves-1b-weapons-aid-for-israel-to-congressional-review-u-s-officials-say/0000018f-7a05-d604-af8f-7f05810c0000</guid></item><item><title>哈佛大学同意讨论中东冲突，学生结束抗议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-15/ty-article/harvard-students-end-protest-as-university-agrees-to-discuss-middle-east-conflict/0000018f-7950-dd07-adbf-fb72a3f60000</link><description>哈佛大学临时校长艾伦·加伯同意就学生的问题举行抗议者和大学官员的会面</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 23:02:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-15/ty-article/harvard-students-end-protest-as-university-agrees-to-discuss-middle-east-conflict/0000018f-7950-dd07-adbf-fb72a3f60000</guid></item><item><title>国防部官员称司法部门拒绝停止对 10 月 7 日事件的调查存在利益冲突</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-15/ty-article/.premium/defense-officials-cry-conflict-of-interest-over-justices-refusal-to-halt-oct-7-probe/0000018f-78ec-d599-ab8f-7cff5ba00000</link><description>批评者认为，最高法院法官吉拉·坎菲·斯坦尼茨的丈夫、前部长尤瓦尔·斯坦尼茨可能会从国家审计长的调查中受益</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 21:26:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-15/ty-article/.premium/defense-officials-cry-conflict-of-interest-over-justices-refusal-to-halt-oct-7-probe/0000018f-78ec-d599-ab8f-7cff5ba00000</guid></item><item><title>以色列官员警告称，随着危机加剧，埃及可能会退出人质交易调解努力</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-15/ty-article/.premium/israeli-officials-caution-that-egypt-may-pull-out-of-hostage-deal-mediation-efforts/0000018f-78e2-d7a4-adcf-fcf7cc1c0000</link><description>由于开罗拒绝允许人道主义援助通过拉法口岸，以色列和埃及之间的危机正在加深，以色列官员也担心国防和情报合作可能被降级</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 21:16:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-15/ty-article/.premium/israeli-officials-caution-that-egypt-may-pull-out-of-hostage-deal-mediation-efforts/0000018f-78e2-d7a4-adcf-fcf7cc1c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列平民在以色列北部被导弹炸死，五名以色列国防军士兵受伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-14/ty-article/.premium/israeli-civilian-killed-by-missile-in-northern-israel-five-idf-soldiers-wounded/0000018f-7899-dd07-adbf-fbfbd9200000</link><description>早些时候，火箭弹向马尔基亚地区发射，引发的大火仍在肆虐，其中一枚发射到西加利利的火箭弹击中了一个监视气球，落入黎巴嫩境内</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 20:21:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-14/ty-article/.premium/israeli-civilian-killed-by-missile-in-northern-israel-five-idf-soldiers-wounded/0000018f-7899-dd07-adbf-fbfbd9200000</guid></item><item><title>在以色列最令人沮丧的独立日，内塔尼亚胡利用阵亡者和人质进行宣传</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-14/ty-article/.premium/on-a-wretched-independence-day-netanyahu-exploited-the-fallen-and-hostages-for-propaganda/0000018f-787e-df8f-a78f-fdff759c0000</link><description>以色列总理和他的妻子因胆怯而缺席国家独立日仪式，他们预先录制了一段讲话，其中没有任何承担责任的暗示——所有电视网络都乐于播出，就像现场直播一样</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 20:13:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-14/ty-article/.premium/on-a-wretched-independence-day-netanyahu-exploited-the-fallen-and-hostages-for-propaganda/0000018f-787e-df8f-a78f-fdff759c0000</guid></item><item><title>在加沙贾巴利亚，没有“后天”战略，以色列士兵再次与哈马斯作战</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-14/ty-article-magazine/.premium/in-gazas-jabalya-with-no-day-after-strategy-israeli-soldiers-fight-hamas-again/0000018f-77e6-df8f-a78f-ffff2f2b0000</link><description>以色列国防军宣布四个多月前“解散”了加沙北部的哈马斯营。现在，以色列军队的整个旅已经返回，他们的经历与他们的对手一样</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 17:24:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-14/ty-article-magazine/.premium/in-gazas-jabalya-with-no-day-after-strategy-israeli-soldiers-fight-hamas-again/0000018f-77e6-df8f-a78f-ffff2f2b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列拒绝讨论加沙战争“第二天”威胁美国的整个中东战略</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-05-14/ty-article/.highlight/israels-refusal-to-discuss-day-after-gaza-war-threatens-americas-mideast-strategy/0000018f-77a3-ddbe-addf-77af6eab0000</link><description>以色列在哈马斯事件后第二天对讨论的顽固态度不仅会危及美国推动进程的努力，而且可能导致大幅倒退，从而产生深远的后果</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 16:14:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-05-14/ty-article/.highlight/israels-refusal-to-discuss-day-after-gaza-war-threatens-americas-mideast-strategy/0000018f-77a3-ddbe-addf-77af6eab0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列处于战争状态，第 221 天​​：埃及考虑因拉法行动降低与以色列的关系</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-14/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-221-egypt-mulls-downgrading-relations-with-israel-over-rafah-op/0000018f-77d2-d430-a38f-f7f640e60000</link><description>国际法院将讨论南非周四针对以色列在拉法的进攻而寻求的新紧急措施 ■ 据报道，拜登政府认为以色列在拉法外集中了足够的兵力，以便在未来几天内进行全面进攻 ■ 卡塔尔总理：就释放人质/停火协议进行谈判由于以色列的拉法行动，局势陷入僵局 ■ 以色列极端分子纵火焚烧了两辆加沙救援卡车 ■ 战争进入 221 天​​后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 16:08:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-14/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-221-egypt-mulls-downgrading-relations-with-israel-over-rafah-op/0000018f-77d2-d430-a38f-f7f640e60000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡部长加入以色列极右翼“向加沙进军”，要求驱逐巴勒斯坦人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-14/ty-article/netanyahu-ministers-join-israeli-far-right-march-to-gaza-demand-palestinians-expulsion/0000018f-778d-d599-ab8f-7fff00c40000</link><description>国家安全部长伊塔马尔·本-格维尔呼吁以色列“鼓励”巴勒斯坦人移出加沙地带；两名越过北部边境进入加沙的抗议者被捕</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 15:07:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-14/ty-article/netanyahu-ministers-join-israeli-far-right-march-to-gaza-demand-palestinians-expulsion/0000018f-778d-d599-ab8f-7fff00c40000</guid></item><item><title>世界法院将就以色列国防军拉法攻势举行听证会；以色列将于周五提出案件</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-05-14/ty-article/world-corut-to-hold-hearings-over-israels-rafah-attacks/0000018f-776a-ddbe-addf-776fbce30000</link><description>南非上周要求联合国法院命令以色列停止拉法入侵后，将于周四在法庭上发言。埃及和土耳其已介入支持此案</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 14:37:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-05-14/ty-article/world-corut-to-hold-hearings-over-israels-rafah-attacks/0000018f-776a-ddbe-addf-776fbce30000</guid></item><item><title>前往加沙的援助车队被以色列极右分子破坏后，巴勒斯坦卡车司机担心安全</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-14/ty-article/palestinian-truckers-fear-for-safety-after-gaza-aid-convoy-wrecked-by-far-right-israelis/0000018f-776a-ddbe-addf-776fd8fe0000</link><description>约旦河西岸卡车司机工会的一名司机表示，大约 15 辆卡车被以色列定居者损坏，他们殴打了一些司机，造成了价值约 200 万美元的损失，而以色列军队或警察没有干预</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 14:28:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-14/ty-article/palestinian-truckers-fear-for-safety-after-gaza-aid-convoy-wrecked-by-far-right-israelis/0000018f-776a-ddbe-addf-776fd8fe0000</guid></item><item><title>两辆运载人道主义援助物资前往加沙的卡车在约旦河西岸起火</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-14/ty-article/.premium/two-trucks-with-humanitarian-aid-bound-for-gaza-set-on-fire-in-the-west-bank/0000018f-75f7-ddbe-addf-77ff80bb0000</link><description>据记录，右翼活动分子将援助卡车上的食物扔在地上，其中两辆卡车后来被烧毁。以色列警方和以色列国防军互相指责对方执法不力，但一名高级安全官员表示，骚乱者收到了“内部消息”</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 09:19:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-14/ty-article/.premium/two-trucks-with-humanitarian-aid-bound-for-gaza-set-on-fire-in-the-west-bank/0000018f-75f7-ddbe-addf-77ff80bb0000</guid></item><item><title>加沙战争中，以色列和平阵营是面临灭亡还是复活？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-14/ty-article/.premium/amid-the-gaza-war-is-israels-pro-peace-camp-facing-extinction-or-resurrection/0000018f-7172-d7ad-abdf-f57eecf90000</link><description>即使没有向参加以色列反战和反内塔尼亚胡抗议活动的大批人群投射左翼反占领幻想，仍然可以肯定地说，越来越多的犹太以色列人对其政府的好战方式感到失望 — — 以至于他们可以可以想象与反抗的、持久的左派达成共同目标</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 09:15:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-14/ty-article/.premium/amid-the-gaza-war-is-israels-pro-peace-camp-facing-extinction-or-resurrection/0000018f-7172-d7ad-abdf-f57eecf90000</guid></item><item><title>报道：真主党指挥官在黎巴嫩南部以色列无人机袭击中丧生，两人死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-14/ty-article-live/u-s-germany-slam-right-wing-israelis-attack-on-gaza-bound-aid-convoy/0000018f-74c8-dd07-adbf-fffa73560000</link><description>以色列平民在北部边境城镇被导弹炸死，五名以色列国防军士兵受伤 ■ 四名以色列国防军士兵在加沙战斗中重伤 ■ 联合国表示，随着以色列国防军坦克深入拉法，超过 50 万人逃离加沙北部拉法 ■ 极右翼内塔尼亚胡部长领导游行呼吁重新安置加沙地带 ■ 报道：埃及官员称开罗考虑降级与以色列的外交关系</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 01:59:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-14/ty-article-live/u-s-germany-slam-right-wing-israelis-attack-on-gaza-bound-aid-convoy/0000018f-74c8-dd07-adbf-fffa73560000</guid></item></channel></rss>